red to previous SDSS data releases. Despite\ntheir low number, DR8 WDMS binaries are found to be dominated by systems\ncontaining cool white dwarfs and therefore represent an important addition to\nthe spectroscopic sample. The updated SDSS DR8 spectroscopic catalogue of WDMS\nbinaries consists of 2316 systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2013 01:13:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
