rowth direction in perovskites may lead to thin films that are relatively\nimmune to distortion effects compared to those grown along [001].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2013 07:14:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 Jun 2013 06:46:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2013 10:01:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-02"}
