z forces and by stresses at the surfaces. The\nfactor of three lower resolution required for convergence in turbulent stresses\nfor our global disk models compared to stratified shearing-boxes is explained\nby this finding. (Abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2013 12:52:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Jun 2013 03:41:39 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2013 07:40:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
