 M_BH-L relation is higher than the\nestimate based on the M_BH-sigma relation and the latter is higher than model\npredictions based on quasar counts, each by about an order of magnitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2013 14:44:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2013 11:45:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2013 15:48:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
